<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="3" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[190,1441,456,545]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,323,456,480]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">Remarks.</emphasis>
Two species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schiner" authorityYear="1866" box="[523,645,457,480]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Eccritosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[523,645,457,480]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">Eccritosia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have been recorded in 
<collectingCountry box="[940,1029,456,480]" name="Mexico" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">Mexico</collectingCountry>
, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Townsend" baseAuthorityYear="1895" box="[1043,1161,457,480]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Eccritosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zamon">
<emphasis box="[1043,1161,457,480]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">E. zamon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ranges from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[192,271,488,512]" name="United States of America" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">U.S.A.</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry box="[305,437,488,512]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Fabricius)" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1787" box="[497,759,488,512]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Eccritosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbata">
<emphasis box="[497,624,488,512]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">E. barbata</emphasis>
(Fabricius)
</taxonomicName>
is distributed from the southeastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1204,1283,488,512]" name="United States of America" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">U.S.A.</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry box="[1317,1441,488,512]" name="Argentina" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Papavero, N." box="[198,384,520,544]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3" pagination="1 - 178" refId="ref8963" refString="Papavero, N. 2009. Catalogue of the Neotropical Diptera: Asilidae. Neotropical Diptera 17: 1 - 178." type="journal article" year="2009">Papavero 2009</bibRefCitation>
). A revision of the genus was made by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lamas, M. G." box="[856,1027,520,544]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3" pagination="45 - 68" refId="ref8209" refString="Lamas, M. G. 1973. A revision of Eccritosia Schiner, 1866 (Diptera, Asilidae). Papeis Avulsos de Zoologia 27 (4): 45 - 68." type="journal article" year="1973">Lamas (1973)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
